00:16:07.860 --> 00:16:09.076
de doenças,

00:16:09.100 --> 00:16:10.316
de crueldade,

00:16:10.340 --> 00:16:11.916
de desumanização,

00:16:11.940 --> 00:16:13.312
de violência.

00:16:13.900 --> 00:16:15.676
Se forem agredidas,

00:16:15.700 --> 00:16:19.156
